00:13:29.380 --> 00:13:30.902
kind of give it to me.

00:13:30.902 --> 00:13:31.860
ROB RITCHIE: All right.

00:13:31.860 --> 00:13:32.440
Hey, thanks, Krist.

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:33.565
KRIST NOVOCELIC: Thank you.

00:13:33.565 --> 00:13:36.568
